    <note>Zhao(1) Yuncheng [10940]  SS, 227.21a (PRC ed. 227.6932). Zheng Xia, WJ, 22.1a-5a (wife, surname Kang, who married him at age 20, thereby becoming the maternal aunt of Zhao(1) Yingzong [9005]). Two daughters became taoist nuns. His son, Zongbao [16840] became the adopted grandson of Yuanxi [16839], whose two sons did not survive to be old enough to be given mingzi. CBD, 4, 3411.</note>
